}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15815/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15815/canvas/1/503e0d7e-af75-4872-93c7-026e2c8dee27","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:13:20.671Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma previously warned Reynolds that she would win a staring contest, in which they now engage. Indeed, this is not only dinner but also a test of wills to see who will break first: will Alma cry out to Reynolds to spit out the mushroom? Will Reynolds commit to swallowing a dish that will cause him immense discomfort? Neither breaks, but Alma takes charge by dictating what will happen to Reynolds and how she will be in control of the situation from now on.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15815/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:728.7021531100478,79.94766746411484,728.5586124401913,901.2716806220095"}}}]}]}]}